{
  "stem": "20684.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "So we went into hiding into a village somewhere with some farmers, and--",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The hiding part, or--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--to escape.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, we weren't prisoners at that stage.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was just the Germans were invading, and they were going.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But we knew exactly what was happening now, because that was a year after-- a year and a half after the-- they invaded Poland originally.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we knew that there was ghetto, Warsaw ghetto, because my uncle and auntie escaped from-- from the Warsaw ghetto.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Told us that their parents were in a very bad way, grandparents.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Had brought the last photographs of them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "At that stage were still all alive, but they were struggling in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we-- so we knew all that was happening, so when the Germans invaded, my father had no problem understanding that this is what was going to happen to us.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Although he didn't expect the invasion.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "No one did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "There was an arrangement, and we're happy to be on the Russian side.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And subsequently we-- we went into-- were taken by some-- also by cart horse, and there was some arrangement was made.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And we finished up in a farm in an attic, hidden in a cupboard about this size.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "A meter high, about more than two meters long, and about a meter wide.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Because I had no problem walking between my parents.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They couldn't walk.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They could only crouch.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "There wasn't high enough-- they could sit and walk, but I could walk between them.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "So we got-- and that cabinet was behind a false wall.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "It was a commercial arrangement.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "My father was buying like rent, running to [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "We didn't see the people that would come in, because no one even in the farm knew that we were there in hiding.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
